rows.label: qst106013_0020
rows.name: Dad, crank up voltage a bit further!

rows.label: qst106013_0030
rows.name:
Tora! Increasing load even
more maybe dangerous!

rows.label: qst106013_0050
rows.name:
We not cross the
line...but we step on it!

rows.label: qst106013_0060
rows.name:
Okay! Kiku! Look closely
at meter doodah!

rows.label: qst106013_0120
rows.name:
Hey, what's this?!
Leaving us in the dark?

rows.label: qst106013_0130
rows.name: I... I can't see a thing!

rows.label: qst106013_0160
rows.name:
The lights went out the first time
we started Hana up too, remember?

rows.label: qst106013_0170
rows.name:
Isn't it...taking a
bit long, though...?

rows.label: qst106013_0210
rows.name:
*hack* *splutter* Was that a
lightning bolt or something?

rows.label: qst106013_0230
rows.name:
I'm okay. But what about
Hana?! How's she doing?!

rows.label: qst106013_0240
rows.name:
Woohoo! Success! Look!
Glorious birth of Hana JD!

rows.label: qst106013_0290
rows.name:
Cool! I'm starting to think
there's something in Tora's
science malarkey after all!

rows.label: qst106013_0300
rows.name:
Hana's an adult now? Talk
about a growth spurt...

rows.label: qst106013_0320
rows.name:
Shut it, Zeke! Unless you want
me to remodel your face!

rows.label: qst106013_0330
rows.name:
Come, Hana! Give us
demonstration of new power!

rows.label: qst106013_0350
rows.name: W-whoa, Hana! Masterpon has own legs!

rows.label: qst106013_0370
rows.name:
Much more efficient like this
when Masterpon travel with Hana.

rows.label: qst106013_0380
rows.name:
This very silly. And big
disrespect to your Masterpon!

rows.label: qst106013_0390
rows.name:
Hahaha! You look like Hana's
little teddy bear there, Tora.

rows.label: qst106013_0420
rows.name: Put Tora down, Hana! Right now!

rows.label: qst106013_0430
rows.name:
Hey, it's not so bad. At least
you don't have to walk.

rows.label: qst106013_0450
rows.name:
Tora is grown-up big adult...
Hana, come on! Hana!!!
